 MS. JANNEY: All right. In all seriousness -- what do you mean? This is j=
ust happening.=20



In all seriousness, my name is Allison Janney and I am here today to draw=
 attention to the opioid epidemic and to celebrate those who are working =
to help others combat substance-use disorder. And I'm actually on a show =
now called "Mom," which deals with people in recovery. And I'm here with =
