<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MS. JANNEY:&nbsp; Hi, every=
one.&nbsp; Good afternoon.&nbsp; I was going to tell you all to be seated, =
but I see you are already seated, so we can begin.&nbsp; Josh is out today.=
